Package org.alljoyn.onboarding.transport

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConnectionResultListener
    A callback for receiving ConnectionResult signal data from devices that support fast switching channel
    OnboardingTransport
    Definition of the Onboarding BusInterface
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectionResult
    Wraps the signal that is emitted when the connection attempt against the personal AP is completed.
    ConnectionResultAJ
    Used for passing ConnectionResult signal over the AllJoyn bus.
    MyScanResult
    A struct that represents a WiFi scan result: SSID and authType.
    OBLastError
    A class that represents the last onboarding error: The last error code and error message
    ScanInfo
    A class that represents a WiFi scan: an array of SSID and authType, with an age
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConnectionResult.ConnectionResponseType
    These enumeration values are returned from a device that supports fast channel switching .It is reported after the device tries to verify the validity of the Wi-Fi parameters received via OnboardingTransport.ConfigureWiFi(String, String, short)
    OnboardingTransport.ConfigureWifiMode
    These enumeration values are used to indicate the ConfigureWifi possible modes
